 <title>Venice Underwater</title>
 <link>http://www.theworldisnotflat.com/venice_flood</link>
 <description>&lt;p&gt;Most people agree that Venice, Italy is sinking, but it&amp;#39;s only about a few millimeters a year.&amp;nbsp; The real problem is that the water is rising more and more each year. We were surprised to arrive and find that a great deal of the city was inaccessible due to floodwaters.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;This short video is not our smoothest effort, but does show you what was happening...&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;

